zion elites that utilizes flame shotguns and plasma-shield technology.\n[*][b]Horizon Cryocraze Hoplites[/b], Horzion elites that specialize in ice spells and lances, as well as plasma-shields.\n[/list]\n\n\n[b]New Planet, Empyrean[/b]\nHome of the Gilten, the [u]Empyrean[/u] is a planet filled with golden rays of light. Visiting travelers are automatically directed to the flying ark looming amongst the clouds, surrounded by sky-islands and ancient ruins.\n\n[u]Notable Enemies[/u]\n[list]\n[*][b]Trispiel[/b], an ancient light being that once guarded the sky-arks.\n[/list]\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/CmXuZTg.png[/img]\n\n[b]New Dungeons[/b]\nSeveral new dungeons are introduced in this update, as well as a new type of dungeon: [u]General Dungeons![/u] These can be found in most Arcana planets except for in Tripolar and Mirage stars.\n\n[u]New Dungeons[/u]\n[list]\n[*][b]Blistering Sanctum[/b] (Blistering)\n[*][b]Windswept Sanctum[/b] (Windswept)\n[*][b]Pearlles Provincial City[/b] (Amorous)\n[*][b]Empyrean Sanctum[/b] (Empyrean)\n[*][b]Gilten Reception Ark[/b] (Empyrean)\n[/list]\n\n[u]New General Dungeons[/u]\n[list]\n[*][b]Koel Industries Outpost[/b] (commonly found in Arcane planets)\n[*][b]Miniknog Research Camp[/b] (commonly found in Arcane planets)\n[/list]\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/CmXuZTg.png[/img]\n\n[b]New Furniture Sets[/b]\n- Romantic Set\n- Studio Set\n- Archaic Set\n\n[b]Texture Changes[/b]\n- Many blocks, items and furniture pieces have received new textures.\n- Most crafting stations now have improved texture as well as the feature of being upgradeable.\n\n[b]Biome Overhauls[/b]\nNumerous biomes have been overhauled and polished. Several planets such as the Superstorm Expanse, Windswept, Stahlern Badlands and Ardent Taiga now have new parallaxes. Planets now have new icons by @eXyter as well!\n\n[b]Planet Merges[/b]\n- Arcane Desert, Arcane Tundra, and Arcane Forest planets have been merged into Arcane planets.\n- Sanguine, Ardent Taiga and Golden Forest are now subbiomes.\n\n[b]Arcana Wiki[/b]\nA WIP Wiki page has been setup for those who need help with obtaining certain items and resources.\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/CmXuZTg.png[/img]\n\n[b]General Improvementsi[/b]\n[list]\n[*]Katanas and Greatswords have been reworked and given new combos.\n[*]Dungeon loots now have a chance of dropping Arcana legendary weapons.\n[*]Several planets now have general encounter dungeons that feature friendly npcs as well as hostile foes.\n[*]New legacy and unused items have been added to the Shady Vendor's shop at Nova Station.\n[/list]\n\nFeaturing:\n[list]\n[*]Greatspear of Light, [b]Luxiant[/b]\n[/list]\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/uF3LNaT.png[/img]\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/ovKdOrd.png[/img]\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/Zgbbl9S.png[/img]\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/GfgiFMb.png[/img]\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/CmXuZTg.png[/img]\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n[h1]Arcana, a Mystical Universe[/h1]\n\nArcana is a growing techno-magic themed Starbound mod that features a vast amount of added content, including:\n\n[list]\n[*]28+ new planets\n\n[*]80+ custom weapons\n\n[*]80+ armor pieces and cosmetics\n\n[*]600+ new tiles and objects\n[/list]\n\nArcana is also constantly updating with new contents, aiming to always provide new magical elements for the star explorers to find.\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/CmXuZTg.png[/img]\n\n\n[h1]New Bosses & Monsters[/h1]\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/QuJiMjr.png[/img]\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/CmXuZTg.png[/img]\n\n\n[h1]An Abundance of New Content[/h1]\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/y4HA0Fb.png[/img]\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/Z8cDBAw.png[/img]\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/EDOWj5N.png[/img]\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/CmXuZTg.png[/img]\n\n\n[h1]New Encounters![/h1]\n\nA new race, new locations, as well as several new weapon types are added.\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/H1ccfPq.png[/img]\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/fIugjCG.png[/img]\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/VpRsTKU.png[/img]\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/CmXuZTg